```python
import re

def palindromes_of_specific_lengths(string):
    substring = string[63:71]
    substring = re.sub('[^a-zA-Z]', '', substring.lower())
    palindromes = set()

    for length in range(4, 6):
        for start in range(len(substring) - length + 1):
            end = start + length
            sub = substring[start:end]
            if sub == sub[::-1]:
                palindromes.add(sub)

    return palindromes
```
